name: Toyosatomimi no Miko 豊聡耳 神子 | Touhou Project
description:
One of my favourite character from Touhou.

Play around with lora's values that suits to you.

Global tag:

ToyoNoMiko

__________________________________________________________________________________________________

  • For v2:

Now it's more flexible and easy to use.

If you want add wanted cloth - lower value to 0.8 or even lower.

default tags: 

earmuffs, skirt, small breasts, short hair, sandals, sleeveless shirt, yellow eyes

additional tags: 

sword, cape

.

Sometimes it creates familiar face over time - it's mostly like an artwork of syuri22 (just be here)

__________________________________________________________________________________________________

  • For rest:

optional tags: purple earmuffs, purple skirt, small breasts, short hair, sandals, sleeveless shirt, yellow eyes

additional tags: sword, cape

Sometimes SD can create purple hair, so add this tag to BL

_

Soft ver: - can create something that looks like her (in most cases - her hair style)

Medium ver: - can create something that looks like in her original or other (same color palette, hair style etc.)

Heavy ver: - in most cases - Toyosatomimi no Miko (skirt, sword, cape, etc...)

_

Btw she is 1449 years old

It's my first lora

_

Trained on around 1000 images from gelbooru (NSFW and SFW).

Tools used:

Dataset Maker by Hollowstrawberry

Lora Trainer by Hollowstrawberry
